    • com.github.davidmoten.rx.internal.operators.OperatorGroupBy<T,K,V>

    K - the key type

    public final class OperatorGroupBy<T,K,V>
extends Object
implements rx.Observable.Operator<rx.observables.GroupedObservable<K,V>,T>
    Groups the items emitted by an Observable according to a specified criterion, and emits these grouped items as Observables, one Observable per group.
